OL,3,CChris Rea, known for festive hit
OL,4,CDriving Home For Christmas, dies age 74
OL,6,FChris Rea, whose hit songs include the
OL,7,Ffestive hit Driving Home For
OL,8,FChristmas, has died at the age of 74.
OL,10,FThe singer-songwriter died in hospital
OL,11,Fon Monday following a short illness,
OL,12,Faccording to a spokesperson for his
OL,13,Ffamily.
OL,15,FA statement on behalf of his wife and
OL,16,Ftwo children reads: "It is with
OL,17,Fimmense sadness that we announce the
OL,18,Fdeath of our beloved Chris.
