OL,6,F"He passed away peacefully in hospital
OL,7,Fearlier today following a short
OL,8,Fillness, surrounded by his family."
OL,10,FThe Middlesbrough-born musician was
OL,11,Fdiagnosed with pancreatic cancer and
OL,12,Fhad his pancreas removed in 2001, and
OL,13,Fin 2016 he suffered a stroke.
OL,15,FRea found fame in the late Seventies
OL,16,Fand Eighties with hits such as Fool
OL,17,F(If You Think It's Over), Let's Dance
OL,18,Fand The Road To Hell.
