OL,6,FTwo of his studio albums, The Road To
OL,7,FHell and Auberge, went to number one
OL,8,Fin the UK.
OL,10,FHis famous song Driving Home For
OL,11,FChristmas was first released in 1986
OL,12,Fas a B-side to his single "Hello
OL,13,FFriend".
OL,15,FTwo years later in 1988 he released a
OL,16,Fre-recorded version which has become a
OL,17,Fclassic during the festive season.
OL,19,FDuring a 2020 episode of Mortimer And
OL,20,FWhitehouse Gone Fishing, Rea spoke
OL,21,Fabout the origin of the song.
