OL,6,F"I was on the dole when I wrote that,"
OL,7,Fhe said.
OL,9,F"My manager had just left me. I'd just
OL,10,Fbeen banned from driving, right. My
OL,11,Fnow wife, Joan, she had to drive down
OL,12,Fto London, picked me up in the Mini,
OL,13,Fand take me home, and that's when I
OL,14,Fwrote it."
OL,16,FThe song peaked at number 10 in the UK
OL,17,Fofficial charts in 2022. For the 2025
OL,18,FChristmas charts, it made the 30th
OL,19,Fspot.
